{"tid":1628432,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修要睇時機","createTime":"2019-10-06T02:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:19:08.000Z","uid":102351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc35901455d39704c5a58df677833a7172227343","tid":1628432,"uid":102351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"好多紅底商鋪都係抵死<br />\n但絕對唔係依家死<br />\n我地一直係我地圈子入面 緊急法成立對於圈子出面既人可能只係微微不滿<br />\n我地依家將裝修範圍擴闊只會為自己製造風波 佢地係蠢 但佢地都好重要<br />\n我地要將呢類蠢人都收納埋先至可以繼續落去<br />\n先將矛頭指番政權政府對手足做過傷害既人<br />\n琴日林奠講完要同暴力割蓆 呢兩日就有人打橫黎講再升級暴力d令佢地驚<br />\n但記唔記得由當初升到今日咁係用左4個月先令香港人接受倒 當大家接受倒神獸未有冷靜期又要再接受升級只會太格硬黎<br />\n手足 繼續維持現狀走多幾日 起碼等大眾冷靜期完 睇埋泛民司法覆核 失敗左到時升級都可以有名號打出黎<br />\nwe are fighting for a period, not a moment"},{"pid":"32110be38bcb15c781ebeccf7565008887af4a4b","tid":1628432,"uid":184581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:50:52.000Z","msg":"唔好批評前線呀<br />\n一批評就話你冷氣機軍師 + 冇出過去現場<br />\n講多幾句就話你左膠+民意撚想割席<br />\n之後話你唔係同路人 要唔要你支持都冇所謂 扣完你帽直接割9你<br />\n<br />\n總之前線係聖人做咩都唔會錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你再講你就係警狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0131c74d8dfc19a6eb8b5dbe3ad8a657861043a2","tid":1628432,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:52:58.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEPY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=975e5c1